|text1     = Observe the {{Color|h|nobold=1|starting point, finish point, the direction of the arrow on the compass, and the distribution of red obstacles}}. {{Color|h|nobold=1|Rotate}} the rings on the compass to {{Color|h|nobold=1|reach the finish point without running into obstacles by following the arrow's directions upon leaving the starting point}}.
